text: Skarphéðinn Guðmundsson (7 April 1930 - 20 January 2003) was an Icelandic ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1960 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1930 births Category:2003 deaths Category:Icelandic male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Iceland Category:Ski jumpers at the 1960 Winter Olympics
